body:
Was anybody awake at like 4-5 in the morning?

I logged on and I saw that Draft Normals was available. I excitedly queued up for it, got into a champ select and then someone failed to ban and dodged. Instead of getting put back in queue, I was thrown back to the menu and Draft Normals had disappeared.

Was it an error? Will Oceania FINALLY be seen as a real region? I&#039;ve been going on and on about Draft Normals for years and to see it enabled and then just as quickly taken away makes me sad... {{champion:32}}
